# Features Components Directory

This directory contains components specific to the FAANG-grade Features page.

## Components:
- HeroScene.tsx - 3D visualization with React Three Fiber
- FeatureCard.tsx - Uniform feature card component
- FeatureGrid.tsx - Responsive grid layout for feature cards
- ComparisonGrid.tsx - 3-column comparison grid
- CTASection.tsx - Call-to-action section with primary/secondary buttons
